    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="1-Goland单步调试"><a href="#1-Goland单步调试" class="headerlink" title="1. Goland单步调试"></a>1. Goland单步调试</h1><h2 id="1-1-Goland侧配置"><a href="#1-1-Goland侧配置" class="headerlink" title="1.1 Goland侧配置"></a>1.1 Goland侧配置</h2><ol>
<li><p>配置代码同步</p>
<p><img src="/golang%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8B%E8%B0%83%E8%AF%95.assets/image-20240823225107371.png" alt="image-20240823225107371"></p>
</li>
<li><p>添加Go Remote</p>
<p><img src="/golang%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8B%E8%B0%83%E8%AF%95.assets/image-20240823225246673.png" alt="image-20240823225246673"></p>
</li>
</ol>
<h2 id="1-2-Linux-侧配置"><a href="#1-2-Linux-侧配置" class="headerlink" title="1.2 Linux 侧配置"></a>1.2 Linux 侧配置</h2><ol>
<li><p>安装go</p>
<p><img src="/golang%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8B%E8%B0%83%E8%AF%95.assets/image-20240823225501448.png" alt="image-20240823225501448"></p>
</li>
<li><p>配置环境变量</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p><img src="/golang%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8B%E8%B0%83%E8%AF%95.assets/image-20240823225711804.png" alt="image-20240823225711804"></p>
<ol start="3">
<li><p>安装dlv</p>
<p><img src="/golang%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8B%E8%B0%83%E8%AF%95.assets/image-20240823225759957.png" alt="image-20240823225759957"></p>
</li>
<li><p>编译用于调试的go二进制</p>
<p><img src="/golang%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8B%E8%B0%83%E8%AF%95.assets/image-20240823225923905.png" alt="image-20240823225923905"></p>
</li>
<li><p>打开2345端口的防火墙</p>
<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">firewall-cmd --add-port=2345/tcp</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p>停服务</p>
<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">systemctl stop xxx.service</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p>服务端开启dlv调试</p>
<p><img src="/golang%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8B%E8%B0%83%E8%AF%95.assets/image-20240823230501230.png" alt="image-20240823230501230"></p>
</li>
</ol>
<h2 id="1-3-踩坑记录"><a href="#1-3-踩坑记录" class="headerlink" title="1.3 踩坑记录"></a>1.3 踩坑记录</h2><p><img src="/golang%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8B%E8%B0%83%E8%AF%95.assets/image-20240823230835485.png" alt="image-20240823230835485"></p>
<h1 id="2-Goland远程执行单元测试"><a href="#2-Goland远程执行单元测试" class="headerlink" title="2. Goland远程执行单元测试"></a>2. Goland远程执行单元测试</h1><ol>
<li><p>全量执行</p>
<p><img src="/golang%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8B%E8%B0%83%E8%AF%95.assets/image-20240823231615455.png" alt="image-20240823231615455"></p>
</li>
<li><p>单个测试文件执行</p>
<p><img src="/golang%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8B%E8%B0%83%E8%AF%95.assets/image-20240823231956910.png" alt="image-20240823231956910"></p>
</li>
</ol>
<p><strong>注意：如果本地单测文件有改动，记得将改动同步上传至远程服务器</strong></p>
